  ('Otherside Metaverse: The Next Digital Frontier', 'MetaverseNews', 'Inside Yuga Labs'' ambitious metaverse project that could change how we think about virtual worlds and digital land.', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/bayc-article4/800/600', ARRAY['Otherside', 'Metaverse', 'Virtual Land'], ARRAY['Metaverse', 'Gaming'], 'https://example.com/otherside-frontier', 'Otherside isn''t just another metaverse project. With Yuga Labs at the helm and major gaming studios involved, this could be the first truly interoperable virtual world...'),
  ('BAYC x BMW: When Web3 Meets Automotive', 'TechCrunch Web3', 'BMW becomes the latest major brand to embrace NFT culture with their Bored Ape partnership.', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/bayc-article5/800/600', ARRAY['BMW', 'Partnerships', 'Brand Collaboration'], ARRAY['Business', 'Marketing'], 'https://example.com/bayc-bmw', 'The collaboration between BAYC and BMW represents a new era of brand partnerships, where digital ownership and real-world utility converge...'),
  ('The Mutant Ape Serum: Mechanics and Rarity', 'NFT Analytics', 'A deep dive into the serum mechanics that created the Mutant Ape Yacht Club and the rarity tiers involved.', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/bayc-article6/800/600', ARRAY['MAYC', 'Serum', 'Rarity'], ARRAY['Collectibles', 'Analysis'], 'https://example.com/mutant-serum', 'When Yuga Labs airdropped serums to BAYC holders, it created one of the most innovative NFT mechanics in the space. Here''s how it worked...'),
  ('Yuga Labs: Building the Future of Digital Ownership', 'Forbes Crypto', 'How a small team turned cartoon apes into a multi-billion dollar empire and what comes next.', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/bayc-article7/800/600', ARRAY['Yuga Labs', 'Business', 'Leadership'], ARRAY['Entrepreneurship', 'Technology'], 'https://example.com/yuga-labs-future', 'From a small project launched by four pseudonymous founders to acquiring CryptoPunks and Meebits, Yuga Labs has become the undisputed leader in NFTs...'),
  ('ApeFest Through the Years: A Visual Journey', 'Event Magazine', 'From the first intimate gathering to Las Vegas spectacles, ApeFest has evolved into the premier NFT event.', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/bayc-article8/800/600', ARRAY['ApeFest', 'Events', 'Community'], ARRAY['Culture', 'Entertainment'], 'https://example.com/apefest-journey', 'ApeFest started as a small meetup in New York City. Today, it''s a multi-day festival with performances from major artists and celebrity appearances...'),
  ('Koda NFTs: The Mysterious Creatures of Otherside', 'NFT World', 'Everything we know about the Kodas, the mysterious beings that inhabit the Otherside metaverse.', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/bayc-article9/800/600', ARRAY['Koda', 'Otherside', 'Lore'], ARRAY['Gaming', 'Collectibles'], 'https://example.com/koda-mystery', 'Kodas are more than just companions in Otherside. These mysterious creatures hold the key to understanding the lore of this expansive metaverse...'),
  ('How BAYC Changed NFT Community Building Forever', 'Web3 Weekly', 'The blueprint for building engaged communities that BAYC established and others now follow.', 'https://picsum.photos/seed/bayc-article10/800/600', ARRAY['Community', 'Strategy', 'Web3'], ARRAY['Marketing', 'Social'], 'https://example.com/bayc-community', 'Before BAYC, NFT projects were about art. After BAYC, they became about community. Here''s how the Bored Ape team created the template everyone follows...');